<h3 class="wp-block-heading">Details &amp; Semester Outlines for BS Biosciences</h3>



<p>BS Biosciences at SZABIST is a four-year program spread over eight semesters and consists of 135 credit hours of teaching (43 courses), an internship of at least six weeks, and a research project. The maximum time limit to complete the BS degree is six years.</p>



